    <item>
      <title>最高法院被要求恢复通过邮寄方式获取堕胎药</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/02/us/politics/supreme-court-mail-abortion-pill.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[联邦上诉法院暂时中止了食品和药物管理局的一项法规，该法规极大地扩大了堕胎药米非司酮的使用范围。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/02/us/politics/supreme-court-mail-abortion-pill.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 02 May 2026 23:16:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法院裁决禁止邮寄药丸后，堕胎服务提供者被迫做出调整</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/02/us/abortion-pill-mifepristone-5th-circuit-court-ruling.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[第五巡回法院的裁决恢复了患者亲自去看医疗保健提供者以获得米非司酮的要求，这颠覆了美国的堕胎准入。该裁决目前正在上诉。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/02/us/abortion-pill-mifepristone-5th-circuit-court-ruling.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 02 May 2026 21:17:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
